A '''''Ng'rhr''''', in the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] culture, was a Wookiee who was the master of an apprentice in a given trade. The word ''"Ng'rhr"'' meant "clan uncle" in [[Shyriiwook/Legends|Shyriiwook]].

In [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], the Wookiee [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Chenlambec]] acted as the ''Ng'rhr'' to [[Tinian I'att Azur-Jamin|Tinian I'att]]. She often referred to him as such both as a sign of respect and affection.

